Stevens, chairman of the John F. Kennedy Center for the Performing
Arts, to the President's Committee on the Arts and Humanities.
   In addition, the president will nominate Jane A. Kenny, now
director of VISTA and student community service programs at the
ACTION agency, as deputy director of ACTION, succeeding Henry A.
Ventura.
